data.description: This like new home is located in Lincoln's Taylors Farm Subdivision.This brick and vinyl exterior features: 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, family room, kitchen, dining area, laundry room and a double garage. Amenities include:  laminate hardwood and tile floors, granite and solid surface countertops, stainless appliances, tile shower in master suite, Open floor and split bedroom floor plan, tray ceiling and walk-in closet in master, vaulted ceiling in the familyroom, Kitchen pantry, linen closets in baths and much much more. The design of this home is simply divine with its craftsman style arthitecture. Your perfect home...... with nothing to do but move your furniture in and enjoy!  This one owner home won't last long!
